          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Frequently Asked Questions\nThe RBC Signature No Limit Banking Account is a chequing account that offers unlimited debit transactions in Canada, valuable savings, and exclusive benefits. You can open this account with no minimum balance and enjoy features like free Interac e-Transfers, monthly fee rebates, and access to RBC Vantage.\nThe standard monthly fee for the RBC Signature No Limit Banking Account is $16.95 2 . You can lower or eliminate this fee by:\nEnrolling in the RBC Value Program and linking other eligible RBC products, such as a credit card or mortgage 24\nTaking advantage of the senior fee rebate 4 , if eligible\nYou can only receive one monthly fee rebate per bank account. For example, you cannot receive both the Value Program Rebate 24 and the Seniors Rebate 4 on the same account in the same month. We automatically apply to your account the highest value rebate you are",
