          "evidence_text_excerpt": "A Chequing account with everyday benefits\nWith RBC Vantage, you can enjoy additional benefits at no extra cost and with no minimum balance required when you open an eligible RBC bank account.\nNo minimum balance\nEarn Avion points 15 on everyday purchases\nFree Interac e-Transfer \u2021 transactions 4, 5\nSave 3\u00a2/L on gas at Petro-Canada 6",
