          "evidence_text_excerpt": "debits for accounts with a limited number of free debits. There is a limit of 999 free Interac e-Transfer Transactions per Month per Account; for every Interac e-Transfer Transaction over the limit, you will be charged $1. For all Canadian dollar savings accounts, transfers through the Interac e-Transfer service are $1 each, count as a Debit Transaction toward any free monthly total and carry an Excess Debit Transaction Fee, if applicable. The Interac e-Transfer service is not available with U.S. Dollar Accounts.\nlegal disclaimer\nThe following debits will not count toward the number of included Debit Transactions per Month: RBC Virtual Visa \u2021 Debits; Self-Serve electronic funds transfers from your personal deposit account to another personal deposit account in your name; pre-authorized or self-service transfers made to any RBC credit card; payments to your RBC Royal Bank personal loan,",
