        {
          "field_name": "eligibility_text",
          "candidate_value": "3) Must maintain a minimum of $5,000 at all",
          "value_type": "string",
          "confidence": 0.55,
          "extraction_method": "heuristic_eligibility_text",
          "source_document_id": "src-rbc-html-17c22b13acaf884e",
          "source_snapshot_id": "snap-e4e4ee03f87d1050",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-127639782cf923f0",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Ready to Invest?\nBuy a GIC for your registered account or on its own.\nBuy a GIC Purchase a Different Investment\nView Legal Disclaimers Hide Legal Disclaimers\nView Legal Disclaimers\nHide Legal Disclaimers\n1)\nThe rate of interest on Interest Rate-Linked GICs is calculated based on a discount from the RBC prime interest rate. The RBC prime interest rate is a reference rate for determining interest rates on Canadian dollar commercial loans in Canada and is subject to change. The RBC prime interest rate can be found at rbcroyalbank.com/rates/prime.html . You may obtain the current interest rate applicable to your Interest Rate-Linked GIC by signing into Online or Mobile Banking, by making inquiries at your local branch, or by calling us at 1-800-463-3863.\n2)\nNo interest is paid if cashed within 29 days and a $25.00 administration fee will apply.\n3)\nMust maintain a minimum of $5,000 at all",
          "anchor_type": "section",
          "anchor_value": "ready-to-invest",
          "page_no": null,
          "chunk_index": 18,
          "field_metadata": {
            "retrieval_mode": "metadata-only",
            "matched_keywords": [
              "apply",
              "can"
            ]
