          "source_snapshot_id": "snap-8df38dd0880417e5",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-4f924df12e333336",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Which high interest savings account is right for you?\nLook for a high interest savings account that balances your savings goals with any withdrawal restrictions or fees. Look for a strong, consistent interest rate\u2014just be sure to read the fine print, as some rates are only promotional. Accounts with no monthly fees, low or no minimum balance requirements, and easy transfers to your chequing account offer added flexibility.\nSince some HISAs are online-only, look for a financial institution that has a strong digital presence, with a user-friendly website and a good mobile app.",
